N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 345.7 - Committee chairman, secretary

State Regulations

The chairman, Workers' Compensation Board, shall designate
a member of the Chiropractic Practice Committee as chairman and shall also
appoint a secretary of such committee. Notes
